{
  "stem": "20684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He turned around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I don't know why he was upset, but he was upset because evidently, the leg belonged to someone that he knew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the rest was not good, the leg was good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I took the leg with me, took it to my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It took me half a day, about maybe three or four hours, to cover 200 or 300 meters because the snow was very soft and I to sink in and the leg used to sink in where the [INAUDIBLE] the leg was toward me.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we would get up and down and I would crawl up the leg and push the leg up and the leg would go down and I would go down.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we kept on going and going, going and it just lasted forever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I thought it was a good game.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was doing something very useful, of course, taking a good leg to my father who was fixing people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I mean, it's one of the best ones there was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I had a good look at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I-- I wasn't stupid, don't worry about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I-- before I found, I took the best leg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, I wouldn't have taken anything-- anything-- anything but the best.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I took that good leg to my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I had to wait for a while, but he came in and the first time I've seen him actually in-- all covered in blood, his white overalls.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was wearing lots of blood and he had blood-- they were operating because some of the wounded were already taken, the ones that were alive.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You see, they got there before me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I mean, it took me six hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They would all die by then.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
